@node Installation "Installation"
        
@{u}Installation@{uu}
        
Copy muu.rexx to rexx:
Copy muue.rexx to rexx:
Copy readsu.rexx to rexx:
Copy smartdecode to somewhere in your path.  i.e. c:
Copy b64d to somewhere in your path.  i.e. c:
        
@endnode
@node QUsage "Quick Usage"

@{u}Quick Usage@{uu}

Usage: rx muue sourcedir destdir workdir

e.g.

@{b}rx muue uunews:comp/binaries/amiga/ data:progs/ t:@{ub}

This scans the directory uunews:comp/binaries/amiga/ for files
to join and then joins and decodes any valid UUencoded files,
decodes any valid base64 files and deletes any files muue
decides are invalid or unknown.

(Invalid files are those that start with RE: in the subject line,
Unknown files are those that do not seem to have a valid subject
line or valid UU or base64 data in)

@endnode

